# references/despachobonsai — local-only reference clone (ML-sync impl). It has its own
# .git, node_modules, .next builds and .env secrets inside; git add silently no-ops on
# nested-repo files, so it stays untracked like design_handoff. To adopt the SOURCE into
# this repo: mv its .git to .git.local, then git add (junk dirs would need re-ignoring).
references/despachobonsai/
